    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The ancient once said...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ancient legends said that a great power was aprisioned in a dungeon, where only the bravest could venture and get out alive. Countless adventurers tried, but never returned to tell the story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Dungeon Full of Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a dungeon filled with challenges to overcome, where patience and agility are key traits for success.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use Rings to Enhance Your Skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find rings as you explore the dungeon and equip the best ones for your playstyle, creating unique and personalized combat experiences for each player.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Distribute Points to Strengthen Yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and earn points to improve your character by choosing attributes that can make you faster or more resistant to enemy attacks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eliminate Hundreds of Enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face and defeat hundreds of enemies guarding the dungeon from intruders, using all the resources acquired during your exploration. But beware of the bosses you'll encounter...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equip Weapons with Unique Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover unique weapons while exploring and defeating bosses. Each weapon contains a distinctive set of abilities that makes combat truly one-of-a-kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Power of Doznath</strong> is a 2D Action RPG where you can choose a class and progress your character, through a challenging dungeon, in order to find a great power once dormant.</p>",
